snippet.title: ELYPSE | Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Embark upon a tragic tale and discover the ravaged world of Elypse! Fight your destiny in an arduous platforming experience, in a mesmerising and mysterious world. 

Available May 17th on Steam, Epic Games Store and GoG.

#indiegame #platformer 

Wishlist now on Steam : https://bit.ly/3BDeeAr
